data.description: New Construction without the wait!! This stunning home built in 2022 has all the space you need with crisp modern finishes. As you walk through the front door you'll be greeted by the open concept floorplan featuring luxury vinyl plank flooring in all main living areas and upgraded carpet in bedrooms. The kitchen features granite countertops with shaker style cabinets, stainless steel appliances and a grand island overlooking the large family room. Guest bedroom and full bathroom located on the first floor. Heading up to the second story, step into the oversized loft and playroom with plenty of space to truly make this house your home. In addition, you'll find the spacious Master Bedroom and ensuite featuring a double vanity and a large walk in closet! Three additional generous sized bedrooms and full bathroom are also located on the second floor. Situated in the new community of Wiregrass, this home is close to Lake Nona shops and dining as well as the 417 for easy commuting. Call now for your private showing!
